FinalProject

Class NeweggItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • FinalProject.NeweggItem

  • public class NeweggItem
extends Object
    Represents an individual search result on Newegg. The name, price, image, and link to the item are used to create an object with all the necessary information to represent its counterpart on Newegg.
    Author:
    Alexander Creech
